item.title: Purple Sweet Potato Powder (50g)
item.description: Điện cơ Thanh Hiền Purple Sweet Potato powder Điện cơ Thanh Hiền Purple Sweet Potato powder is carefully picked and processed from the most fresh and best raw vegetables grown in our own farm in Lam Dong. Our products are produced by SEFD technology (patent pending) and is certified by Vietnam Food Safety regulator. Ingredients: 100% Purple Sweet Potato No flavor or additive added Benefits: Rich in carbohydrates, fiber, beta-carotene (vitamin A carotenoids), vitamin C, vitamin B6, iron, manganese and potassium.
